plate to archive product, categories, tags and single product page.</li>\\n<li>Include standard WooCommerce LayersWP widgets (Product title, prices, ratings, etc).</li>\\n<li>Easy custom styling for each WooCommerce LayersWP widget.</li>\\n</ul>\\n\\n<h2 id=\\"item-description__changelog\\">Changelog:</h2>\\n\\n\\t<p><strong>Version 1.0.5 &#8211; 24/03/2016</strong></p>\\n\\n\\n<pre>\\n- Bug fixes and plugin compatibility with latest Layers version 1.2.14\\n</pre>\\n\\n\\t<p><strong>Version 1.0.4 &#8211; 23/02/2016</strong></p>\\n\\n\\n<pre>\\n- Bug fixes and plugin compatibility with latest Layers version 1.2.13\\n</pre>\\n\\n\\t<p><strong>Version 1.0.3 &#8211; 28/09/2015</strong></p>\\n\\n\\n<pre>\\n- Minor bug fixes conflict with Woosh Slider - Layers extension plugin.\\n- Added 2 new product display hover style ( Half overlay and Slide Hover ).\\n- Fix minor responsive css.\\n- Show admin notice when current theme is not Layers theme or Layers child theme.\\n</pre>\\n\\n\\t<p><strong>Version 1.0.2 &#8211; 12/09/2015</strong></p>\\n\\n\\n<pre>- Bug fixes on single product template view redirection.\\n- Make template redirection on wp customize page instead of on its iframe preview page.\\n- Fix bug global var $product return string issue.\\n- UI improvement custom sidebar builder add new button css style.</pre>\\n\\n\\t<p><strong>Version 1.0.1 &#8211; 28/08/2015</strong></p>\\n\\n\\n<pre>- Added display post state in admin column title to identify that this post is WooLayers Template.\\n- Added quick access customize link admin bar menu on product single or archive product which has WooLayers Template.\\n- Sorting Bar widget: Apply custom text color only to text element\\n- Single Price Widget: Separate custom color for regular price and sale price.\\n- Single Product Thumbnails Widget: Added design bar column options.\\n- Added sidebar builder row Remove/Add gutter option.\\n- Added new template assignment option for custom product tag pages.\\n- Added new Layer